Package com.nokia.places.media

The media package provides classes to describe the data objects associated with an individual place, such as media images and reviews

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Editorial
    This interface represents editorial content about a Place.
    EditorialPage
    This interface represents a paginated list of editorial reviews from professional companies .
    Image
    This interface represents media images of views and points of interest within a Place.
    ImagePage
    The response to a request for a paginated list of Image items
    Review
    This interface represents review content that provides access to user reviews and ratings about a Place.
    ReviewPage
    This interface represents the response to a request for a paginated list of Review items.
